## Summary: What's Required vs Optional

| Component | Required? | What happens without it |
|-----------|-----------|------------------------|
| **Supabase** | вҡЎ REQUIRED for persistence | Demo mode вҖ” analysis works but data lost on restart |
| **Redis** | вҡЎ REQUIRED for Celery | Background tasks won't run (sync fallback works) |
| **pip install** | вҡЎ REQUIRED | Backend won't start |
| **npm install** | вң… Already done | вҖ” |
| **Neo4j** | Optional | Graph risk returns demo data |
| **Ollama** | Optional | CAM uses template text instead of AI narrative |
| **ML model training** | Optional | Uses heuristic formula instead of XGBoost |
| **PyMuPDF/pdfplumber** | Optional | PDF parsing unavailable, but TXT/Excel work |
| **Docker** | Optional | Can run everything manually instead |
